This is a example using:
Mojolicious::Lite
EV
AnyEvent::IRC
AnyEvent::IRC::Client
DateTime

It is a irc logging bot that connects to irc.perl.org and log's the channel mojo
you can change the configuration manually or with the web browser.

to install first install the dependieces which are listed above.
Then type :
morbo log.pl

in the terminal.

and in your web browser go to 127.0.0.1:3000


I hope you enjoy :)
